<text><body>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0239a16" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0239a17" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0239a18" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 610</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0239a19" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title><note n="0239002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0239002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛說【大】＊，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0239002"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>內身觀章句<note n="0239003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（一卷）【宮】</note><note n="0239003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經【大】，經一卷【宮】</note><app n="0239003"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">經一卷</rdg></app></title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0239a20" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0239a21" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0239004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">失譯…漢錄＝漢失譯【宋】【元】【宮】，漢失譯師名【明】</note><note n="0239004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">失譯…漢錄【大】，漢失譯【宋】【元】【宮】，漢失譯師名【明】</note><app n="0239004" cb:word-count="8"><lem wit="【大】">失譯人名在後漢錄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">漢失譯</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">漢失譯師名</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0239a22" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><lg xml:id="lgT15p0239a2201"><l>一切一其心，<caesura/>皆聽美言訓，</l>
<lb n="0239a23" ed="T"/><l>佛所<note n="0239005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">從＝行【宮】</note><note n="0239005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">從【大】，行【宮】</note><app n="0239005"><lem wit="【大】">從</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">行</rdg></app>得道，<caesura/>且聽我彼經。</l>
<lb n="0239a24" ed="T"/><l>彼空亦不斷，<caesura/>有行皆非常，</l>
<lb n="0239a25" ed="T"/><l>夫行不敗壞，<caesura/>佛以講授經。</l>
<lb n="0239a26" ed="T"/><l>深微難見事，<caesura/>非章原之句，</l>
<lb n="0239a27" ed="T"/><l>通彼能敷演，<caesura/>是以故為師。</l>
<lb n="0239a28" ed="T"/><l>從本以存本，<caesura/>有造法之積，</l>
<lb n="0239a29" ed="T"/><l>從慧以除棄，<caesura/>上士所講說。</l>
<pb n="0239b" ed="T" xml:id="T15.0610.0239b"/>
<lb n="0239b01" ed="T"/><l>所從因緣有，<caesura/>有行皆無有，</l>
<lb n="0239b02" ed="T"/><l>亦有前世<note n="0239006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">除＝除【元】【明】</note><note n="0239006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">除【大】，除【元】【明】</note><app n="0239006"><lem wit="【大】">除</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】"><!--CBETA todo type: None-->除</rdg></app>，<caesura/>無知彼諸行；</l>
<lb n="0239b03" ed="T"/><l>亦如欲演身，<caesura/>日親之所講，</l>
<lb n="0239b04" ed="T"/><l><note n="0239007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝夫【三】，大災＝夫裁【宮】</note><note n="0239007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大災【大】，夫裁【宮】，夫災【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0239007"><lem wit="【大】">大災</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">夫裁</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">夫災</rdg></app>患無數，<caesura/>皆以歸流身。</l>
<lb n="0239b05" ed="T"/><l>刪定如本文，<caesura/>所演眾要言，</l>
<lb n="0239b06" ed="T"/><l>靡麗五字句，<caesura/>明誓以勸勉。</l>
<lb n="0239b07" ed="T"/><l>以頌文具足，<caesura/>偶字音商備，</l>
<lb n="0239b08" ed="T"/><l>若花實雜<note n="0239008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">糅＝采【宮】</note><note n="0239008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">糅【大】，采【宮】</note><app n="0239008"><lem wit="【大】">糅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">采</rdg></app>，<caesura/>皆聽彼我誨。</l>
<lb n="0239b09" ed="T"/><l>身非人非命，<caesura/>不丈夫非士，</l>
<lb n="0239b10" ed="T"/><l>若體若<note n="0239009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＝有【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不【大】，有【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239009"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">有</rdg></app>艶，<caesura/>斯事都無彼。</l>
<lb n="0239b11" ed="T"/><l>夫身造而有，<caesura/>以有即敗亡，</l>
<lb n="0239b12" ed="T"/><l>無強皆歸<note n="0239010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">命＝終【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">命【大】，終【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239010"><lem wit="【大】">命</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">終</rdg></app>，<caesura/>如沫蹈踐碎；</l>
<lb n="0239b13" ed="T"/><l>無強則無常，<caesura/>無常即無樂；</l>
<lb n="0239b14" ed="T"/><l>無常亦為苦，<caesura/>非身身非我；</l>
<lb n="0239b15" ed="T"/><l>身非常亦苦，<caesura/>非彼應為身。</l>
<lb n="0239b16" ed="T"/><l><note n="0239011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若＝苦【宮】</note><note n="0239011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">若【大】，苦【宮】</note><app n="0239011"><lem wit="【大】">若</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">苦</rdg></app>體艶我有，<caesura/>身都無可有；</l>
<lb n="0239b17" ed="T"/><l>若以都無體，<caesura/>有存亦有亡。</l>
<lb n="0239b18" ed="T"/><l>慧者以本末，<caesura/>何彼已有體？</l>
<lb n="0239b19" ed="T"/><l>若以無<note n="0239012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">主＝生【宮】</note><note n="0239012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">主【大】，生【宮】</note><app n="0239012"><lem wit="【大】">主</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">生</rdg></app>者，<caesura/>不得以自由，</l>
<lb n="0239b20" ed="T"/><l>有校計若此，<caesura/>何彼體我有？</l>
<lb n="0239b21" ed="T"/><l>斯體身為空，<caesura/>體我有為虛，</l>
<lb n="0239b22" ed="T"/><l>應因緣為有，<caesura/>非身逝心造，</l>
<lb n="0239b23" ed="T"/><l>非眾人身造，<caesura/>亦非自身造，</l>
<lb n="0239b24" ed="T"/><l>都無<note n="0239013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">身有＝有身【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">身有【大】，有身【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239013"><lem wit="【大】">身有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">有身</rdg></app>造，<caesura/>亦身<note n="0239014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無不＝不無【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無不【大】，不無【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239014"><lem wit="【大】">無不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">不無</rdg></app>造。</l>
<lb n="0239b25" ed="T"/><l>以身無造者，<caesura/>從彼為得諦。</l>
<lb n="0239b26" ed="T"/><l>亦非都骨節，</l>
<lb n="0239b27" ed="T"/><l>從前世方來，<caesura/>亦非天造身，</l>
<lb n="0239b28" ed="T"/><l>非神所化<note n="0239015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">城＝成【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">城【大】，成【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239015"><lem wit="【大】">城</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">成</rdg></app>，<caesura/>非無行無本，</l>
<lb n="0239b29" ed="T"/><l>無因為自有，<caesura/>是身有所由，</l>
<pb n="0239c" ed="T" xml:id="T15.0610.0239c"/>
<lb n="0239c01" ed="T"/><l>有事亦有<note n="0239016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">物＝初【宮】</note><note n="0239016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">物【大】，初【宮】</note><app n="0239016"><lem wit="【大】">物</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">初</rdg></app>。<caesura/>有本有所起，</l>
<lb n="0239c02" ed="T"/><l>稍稍為生有，<caesura/>本以癡亦愛，</l>
<lb n="0239c03" ed="T"/><l>心與愛有漏，<caesura/>亦有縛亦結，</l>
<lb n="0239c04" ed="T"/><l>行二品為漏。<caesura/>斯為本亦餘，</l>
<lb n="0239c05" ed="T"/><l>世與受因緣，<caesura/>以由彼斯身，</l>
<lb n="0239c06" ed="T"/><l>以漸能致有。<caesura/>初<note n="0239017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">始＝如【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">始【大】，如【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239017"><lem wit="【大】">始</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">如</rdg></app>有精沫，</l>
<lb n="0239c07" ed="T"/><l>精沫為轉凝，<caesura/>足為生<note n="0239018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">兩＝雨【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0239018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">兩【大】＊，雨【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0239018"><lem wit="【大】">兩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">雨</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0239018"><lem wit="【大】">兩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">雨</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb n="0239c08" ed="T"/><l>以<app type="star" corresp="#0239018"><lem wit="【大】">兩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">雨</rdg></app>為轉厚，<caesura/>以序有四體，</l>
<lb n="0239c09" ed="T"/><l>為生頭第五，<caesura/>若干骨積聚，</l>
<lb n="0239c10" ed="T"/><l>從行為用成，<caesura/>頭九為髑髏，</l>
<lb n="0239c11" ed="T"/><l>頞䪼為二骨，<caesura/>齒根三十二，</l>
<lb n="0239c12" ed="T"/><l>齒三十二骨，<caesura/>頸為與<note n="0239019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耳＝身【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耳【大】，身【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239019"><lem wit="【大】">耳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">身</rdg></app>本，</l>
<lb n="0239c13" ed="T"/><l>鼻為與上腭，<caesura/>心與頸嚨喉，</l>
<lb n="0239c14" ed="T"/><l>凡為骨<note n="0239020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">八十＝十八【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">八十【大】，十八【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239020"><lem wit="【大】">八十</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">十八</rdg></app>。<caesura/>頰車與頸四，</l>
<lb n="0239c15" ed="T"/><l>咽亦為骨四，<caesura/>左臂與右臂，</l>
<lb n="0239c16" ed="T"/><l>凡有骨五十。<caesura/>若其斯左脇，</l>
<lb n="0239c17" ed="T"/><l>應有十三肋；<caesura/>亦斯右脇然，</l>
<lb n="0239c18" ed="T"/><l>應有肋十三，<caesura/>斯為四十八。</l>
<lb n="0239c19" ed="T"/><l>三三三相連，<caesura/>二為二相連，</l>
<lb n="0239c20" ed="T"/><l>其餘不相連，<caesura/>身者以為<note n="0239021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">彊＝疆【明】＊</note><note n="0239021" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->彊【大】＊，疆【明】＊</note><app n="0239021"><lem wit="【大】">彊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">疆</rdg></app>。</l>
<lb n="0239c21" ed="T"/><l>如束葦無彊，<caesura/>脊膂三十二，</l>
<lb n="0239c22" ed="T"/><l>尻與腰為三，<caesura/>若其斯左<note n="0239c2201" resp="CBETA" type="add">髀【CB】【麗-CB】【磧-CB】，脾【大】</note><app n="0239c2201"><lem wit="【CB】【麗-CB】【磧-CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">髀<note type="cf1">K30n1011_p0344c20</note><note type="cf2">Q28_p0290b23</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">脾</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb n="0239c23" ed="T"/><l>骨為二十五；<caesura/>右髀為亦然，</l>
<lb n="0239c24" ed="T"/><l>為骨二十五；<caesura/>肩<note n="0239022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">髀＝<space quantity="1" unit="chars"/>【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">髀【大】，<space quantity="1" unit="chars"/>【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>髀有骨四，</l>
<lb n="0239c25" ed="T"/><l>凡三百二十。<caesura/>敷演<note n="0239023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">名＝各【宮】</note><note n="0239023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">名【大】，各【宮】</note><app n="0239023"><lem wit="【大】">名</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">各</rdg></app>之諦，</l>
<lb n="0239c26" ed="T"/><l>佛以日斷嗣，<caesura/>彼叚悉以聚，</l>
<lb n="0239c27" ed="T"/><l>諸根<note n="0239024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">為以＝以為【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">為以【大】，以為【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239024"><lem wit="【大】">為以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">以為</rdg></app>縫，<caesura/>非瘡而裹之，</l>
<lb n="0239c28" ed="T"/><l>肉血以塗<note n="0239025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">𢴉＝身【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">𢴉【大】，身【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239025"><lem wit="【大】">𢴉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">身</rdg></app>，<caesura/>如木機關縷，</l>
<lb n="0239c29" ed="T"/><l>為如幻師幻。<caesura/>骨機關亦然，</l>
<pb n="0240a" ed="T" xml:id="T15.0610.0240a"/>
<lb n="0240a01" ed="T"/><l>以筋纏縛成，<caesura/>合聚骨若此，</l>
<lb n="0240a02" ed="T"/><l>以為是形體。<caesura/>愚者莫不著，</l>
<lb n="0240a03" ed="T"/><l>智者而不著。<caesura/>生革以隱蔽，</l>
<lb n="0240a04" ed="T"/><l>九孔為大瘡，<caesura/>周匝為滲漏，</l>
<lb n="0240a05" ed="T"/><l>不淨腐臭處，<caesura/>口<note n="0240a0501" resp="CBETA" type="add">喙【CB】【麗-CB】，啄【大】</note><app n="0240a0501"><lem wit="【CB】【麗-CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">喙<note type="cf1">K30n1011_p0345a05</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">啄</rdg></app>如為孔，</l>
<lb n="0240a06" ed="T"/><l>滿之以諸穀，<caesura/>是身為若此。</l>
<lb n="0240a07" ed="T"/><l>以進若干<note n="0240001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">腑＝腐【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">腑【大】，腐【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240001"><lem wit="【大】">腑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">腐</rdg></app>，<caesura/>毛髮與爪齒，</l>
<lb n="0240a08" ed="T"/><l>塵埃亦皮革，<caesura/>骨節亦骨髓，</l>
<lb n="0240a09" ed="T"/><l>為凡筋與脈，<caesura/>胃與心亦脾，</l>
<lb n="0240a10" ed="T"/><l>大腸亦小腸，<caesura/>肝與肺亦腎，</l>
<lb n="0240a11" ed="T"/><l>脂<note n="0240002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">𦠻＝𦙽【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">𦠻【大】，𦙽【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240002"><lem wit="【大】">𦠻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">𦙽</rdg></app>亦大便，<caesura/>淚與唾亦<note n="0240003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">汗＝污【三】</note><note n="0240003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">汗【大】，污【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0240003"><lem wit="【大】">汗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">污</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb n="0240a12" ed="T"/><l>鼻涕膏亦血，<caesura/>寒熱肪小便，</l>
<lb n="0240a13" ed="T"/><l><note n="0240004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text"><g ref="#CB02965"/>＝腦【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0240004" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><g ref="#CB02965"/>【大】＊，腦【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0240004"><lem wit="【大】"><g ref="#CB02965"/></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">腦</rdg></app>之與<app type="star" corresp="#0240004"><lem wit="【大】"><g ref="#CB02965"/></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">腦</rdg></app>膜，<caesura/>皆以沈沒彼，</l>
<lb n="0240a14" ed="T"/><l>如泥塗老牛，<caesura/>如其成不知。</l>
<lb n="0240a15" ed="T"/><l>身之內與外，<caesura/>夫城骨與牆，</l>
<lb n="0240a16" ed="T"/><l>肉血為塗嚴，<caesura/>為怨所破壞。</l>
<lb n="0240a17" ed="T"/><l>恒為以內外，<caesura/>彼<note n="0240005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">央＝中【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">央【大】，中【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240005"><lem wit="【大】">央</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">中</rdg></app>若<note n="0240006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">干＝千【元】【明】【宮】</note><note n="0240006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">干【大】，千【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240006"><lem wit="【大】">干</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】【宮】">千</rdg></app>百，</l>
<lb n="0240a18" ed="T"/><l>以為貪其肉，<caesura/>其外亦災害，</l>
<lb n="0240a19" ed="T"/><l>皆以多尤彼，<caesura/>斯身腐敗壞。</l>
<lb n="0240a20" ed="T"/><l>譬如久故城，<caesura/>晝夜供<note n="0240007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">侍＝待【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">侍【大】，待【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240007"><lem wit="【大】">侍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">待</rdg></app>之，</l>
<lb n="0240a21" ed="T"/><l>壞如已復壞，<caesura/>如坎與空聚；</l>
<lb n="0240a22" ed="T"/><l>恒盜賊俱止，<caesura/>取之欺殆人，</l>
<lb n="0240a23" ed="T"/><l>身為毒虺穴，<caesura/>夫毒虺劇毒；</l>
<lb n="0240a24" ed="T"/><l>恒于身居止，<caesura/>喜怒<note n="0240008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">毒＝恚【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">毒【大】，恚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240008"><lem wit="【大】">毒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">恚</rdg></app>奸<note n="0240009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">弊＝蔽【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">弊【大】，蔽【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240009"><lem wit="【大】">弊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">蔽</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb n="0240a25" ed="T"/><l>孚不和大毒。<caesura/>正使滿百歲，</l>
<lb n="0240a26" ed="T"/><l>恒以和安隱，<caesura/>忿則無<note n="0240010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">反＝返【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">反【大】，返【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240010"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">返</rdg></app>復，</l>
<lb n="0240a27" ed="T"/><l>須臾<note n="0240011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">復＝頃【宮】</note><note n="0240011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">復【大】，頃【宮】</note><app n="0240011"><lem wit="【大】">復</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">頃</rdg></app>不安。<caesura/>斯身為災禍，</l>
<lb n="0240a28" ed="T"/><l>嫌而有恐畏，<caesura/>如虎遊荒澤，</l>
<lb n="0240a29" ed="T"/><l>有畏多恐怖。<caesura/>諸念為以仰，</l>
<pb n="0240b" ed="T" xml:id="T15.0610.0240b"/>
<lb n="0240b01" ed="T"/><l>為一切苦器，<caesura/>亦為諸劇事。</l>
<lb n="0240b02" ed="T"/><l>斯身主為受，<caesura/>沈於苦之法，</l>
<lb n="0240b03" ed="T"/><l>一切諸病宅，<caesura/>為老死之法。</l>
<lb n="0240b04" ed="T"/><l>身為增恩愛，<caesura/>苦以寒與熱，</l>
<lb n="0240b05" ed="T"/><l>或風而不和，<caesura/>是則病<note n="0240012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如＝始【明】</note><note n="0240012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如【大】，始【明】</note><app n="0240012"><lem wit="【大】">如</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">始</rdg></app>生。</l>
<lb n="0240b06" ed="T"/><l>為敗壞諸根，<caesura/><note n="0240013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">失＝夫【元】【明】</note><note n="0240013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">失【大】，夫【元】【明】</note><app n="0240013"><lem wit="【大】">失</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">夫</rdg></app>疾賊害人，</l>
<lb n="0240b07" ed="T"/><l>老死笮厄人，<caesura/>如雪聚得火，</l>
<lb n="0240b08" ed="T"/><l>疾而為解釋。<caesura/>斯若此無數，</l>
<lb n="0240b09" ed="T"/><l>身之多災禍，<caesura/>吾所演一切，</l>
<lb n="0240b10" ed="T"/><l>未能已備具。<caesura/>要以為諸苦，</l>
<lb n="0240b11" ed="T"/><l>腐身為不實，<caesura/>多因緣以成，</l>
<lb n="0240b12" ed="T"/><l>大<note n="0240014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耶＝邪【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耶【大】，邪【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240014"><lem wit="【大】">耶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">邪</rdg></app>以為<note n="0240015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">軀＋（十一因緣章…得道疾）百二十四字卷末別出【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240015" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: a--><!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->軀＋（十一因緣章…得道疾）百二十四字卷末別出【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>軀。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0240b13" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead><title><app type="star" corresp="#0239002"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>內身觀章句<note n="0240016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（一卷）【宋】【宮】</note><note n="0240016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經【大】，經一卷【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0240016"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">經一卷</rdg></app></title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0240b14" ed="T"/><cb:div type="w"><head>十一因緣章</head>
<lb n="0240b15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT15p0240b1501">佛言：「行者有十一因緣，滅道制令<note n="0240017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">人＝入【宋】</note><note n="0240017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">人【大】，入【宋】</note><app n="0240017"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">入</rdg></app>不
<lb n="0240b16" ed="T"/>墮<note n="0240018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔惡〕－【宮】</note><note n="0240018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惡【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0240018"><lem wit="【大】">惡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>道，當不識者，謂萬物。一為大會，謂
<lb n="0240b17" ed="T"/>人眾；二者多食，謂諸美，亦謂過飽；三者為
<lb n="0240b18" ed="T"/>多行，謂多業；四為多<note n="0240019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔喧〕－【宮】</note><note n="0240019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">喧【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0240019"><lem wit="【大】">喧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，謂多語；五為多
<lb n="0240b19" ed="T"/>睡眠；六為會聚，謂禪中；七為習行，謂多事；
<lb n="0240b20" ed="T"/>八為愛身；九為輕，謂非法語；十為貪，謂多
<lb n="0240b21" ed="T"/>欲；十一為不好善處居，謂惡人中。行道者
<lb n="0240b22" ed="T"/>當斷是十一因緣，得道疾。」</p></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>
